parameters:
I feel a sense of peace in the warmth of the bonfire.... My
stamina has fully recovered!

So you've come all the way here. It was quite a task to
prepare the bonfire...

The boss here... isn't it too overpowered?! I don't think
there's anything I can say from my perspective.

\SE[4]This is the end. \!\SE[0]I've torn apart that a few
times before, but it always ended up like this.

\SE[14]Is it always like this...!? \SE[37]But still, I'm
glad to be with both of you... \SE[6]I couldn't handle it
alone...
\SE[5]I wonder if Meria-chan will be saved with this...?

\SE[2]I think so. \SE[0]The cause of that has been taken
care of...

\SE[4]Ah, this place is collapsing too. \SE[3]Since the
master of the sickbed is gone. It will be erased by the
self-purification process.

\SE\SE[15]Next... let's meet in Lunaroa's Dream. \SE[15]I'll
be waiting there with that child.

\SE\SE[2]I'm doing well. \SE[2]They are very kind to us.
Sometimes, though, they have a very lonely expression.

\SE\SE[15]It's time to say goodbye soon. \SE[16]It was a
short time, but it was fun. \SE[15]See you again, Laura.

\SE[23]Luna... I'm going to see you soon. \SE[12]Just a
little longer... Wait for me...

\SE[2]...Soon, this place will collapse. Let's escape.
\SE[1]Come on, take my hand...
